  "hints": [
    {
      "content": "We want to put the largest digit in the highest place value. \n\nWhich digit is the largest? ",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "$\\maroonD8$ is the largest digit, and we want to put it in the position with the highest place value.   \n\nSo $\\maroonD8$ will be in the hundreds place: \n $\\maroonD{8}~\\_~\\_$.",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "Now we need to do the same thing with the next largest digit:  $\\blueE7$.  \n\nSo $\\blueE7$ goes in the tens place:  \n\n$\\maroonD{8}~\\blueE7~\\_$   ",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "The smallest digit is the $\\purpleD1$.  The  $\\purpleD1$ goes in the ones place:  \n\n$\\maroonD{8}\\blueE7\\purpleD1$\n",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    },
    {
      "content": "The greatest possible number we can make is $\\maroonD{8}\\blueE7\\purpleD1$.",
      "images": {},
      "replace": false,
      "widgets": {}
    }
